title: All of Me
description: Sean O'Leary is focused on growing his medical practice. Cat Taylor-Rose revels in her bohemian lifestyle and her burgeoning art career. The two couldn't be more opposite. But Sean just can't stop lusting after the quirky artist, even though he knows he shouldn't.When the inevitable happens, Cat and Sean burn up the sheets, but can they find common ground outside the bedroom? pg. 88
author: Kelsey Maxwell
